description:
This award is for 3 winners, who make the most noise and stands out the most by promoting our space! 
We are really curious about what people gonna do, to bring more CryptoFunk into the community. 

To decide who is going to win, we'll sit down as a team and try to look at every post. 

Winners will be announced on Friday 15th in the afternoon.
You can only be a winner if you are member of CryptoFunk space and follow us on Twitter!

If you are new here: follow on Twitter -> @cryptofunk_NFT 
Be Member of CryptoFunk space!
If you make noise, don't forget to TAG @cryptofunk_NFT.
name: Make some noise for CryptoFunk
